query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(CASE WHEN smshubActivationId = phoneNumber THEN 1 END) as invalidos,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN smshubActivationId != phoneNumber THEN 1 END) as validos,
  COUNT(*) as total
FROM activations 
WHERE apiId = 2
